Final Vision Statement

KasiFit is a gamified health platform that transforms healthy living into a community-driven challenge. Users complete daily health quests, maintain streaks, earn ranks, participate in local activities, and compete alongside their communities, making healthy habits engaging, social, and sustainable for young people in South African townships.
